dialogue: ...Then we film our clients so prospective dates can screen each other for compatibility.
For an extra fee we supply special effects to make you appear more manly.
Our most popular theme is where we dress you in a loin cloth and you rip the arms off an Arnold Schwarzenegger dummy while bombs explode nearby!
Gosh, don't you have something that will make me look sensitive and caring?
Okay... we dress you up as Mary Tyler Moore and have you bottle-feeding this plastic dying dolphin.
No, too sensitive. Suppose we say the dolphin just has a bad cold...
